Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Peace in Europe has been shattered by the largest European land war since the fall of Nazi Germany... It would not have happened if I was president. In the Middle East, the Jewish people have suffered the worst atrocities and deadliest attacks since the Holocaust. The United States has been forced to abandon more embassies under Comrade Kamala than any time in our history... The world is on fire, and Kamala and Biden have marched us to the brink of World War III."
